# Flutter UI 框架和 Android、IOS通信

1.Flutter 中UI变化不会像Android中redraw View 而是重新构建一个新的实例

2.Flutter 中UI更新是通过修改State来触发Widget的绘制

3.StatelessWidgets和StatelessWidget 区别是在于是否有状态需要改变

`If you want to dynamically change the UI based on data received after making an HTTP call or user interaction then you have to work with StatefulWidget and tell the Flutter framework that the widget’s State has been updated so it can update that widget.`

4.当子控件是有状态的，父控件可以是无状态的，不需要保持一致，

5.在Flutter是不可以直接改变的，需要通过操作父Widget来返回不同的view

6.Flutter中使用navigator和route来进行页面导航

Navigator:导航到指定的页面

Route:导航到匿名的界面，使用键值对进行映射

使用已存在的插件进行图片选择和文件读取 `https://pub.dartlang.org/flutter/`

7.MethodChannel的使用

8.Android中使用背景线程
AsyncTask/LiveDate/IntentService/JobScheduler

9.The MyAppBar widget creates a Container with a height of 56 device-independent pixels with an internal padding of 8 pixels, both on the left and the right.


Flutter UI 使用没有UI界面的任务和底层通信(non-UI Task)

